{"tid":2014212,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"第一手天元！黑嘉嘉NHK開課教「美的形狀」 首位海外棋士成固定班底","createTime":"2020-05-13T01:14:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-13T03:17:47.000Z","uid":32511,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5e36e6857e6ec7c0afa3e44058fa4a681077ec52","tid":2014212,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T01:14:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/b40Kwt8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fb40Kwt8.jpg&h=3ec6cfea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nNHK‧ETV的節目「圍棋焦點（日文為：囲碁フォーカス）」從這個春天起，展開了1個由台灣人氣女性棋士黑嘉嘉七段講解的「迷你講座（日文為：ミニレッスン）」單元。根據該電視台表示，此為首次有海外組織的職業棋士固定上節目。<br />\n <br />\n　　迷你講座是有關於「美的形狀」，黑嘉嘉以中文時而交雜著日文進行解說。招牌台詞是搭配上動作的「beautiful shape!」。根據節目負責人員表示，收到了「中文的聲音很可愛」、「招牌台詞帶有意外性，很有趣」、「想要迅速地學會圍棋」一一等的迴響。<br />\n <br />\n　　黑嘉嘉七段則發表感想表示：「希望能以這個節目作為契機，讓日本的大家變得喜歡圍棋。」等。"},{"pid":"9c33cf7c0f0ad36f2e871131334573b1b1c15ed6","tid":2014212,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T01:15:17.000Z","msg":"個頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2d03c190510f731bf9eb86abc263133f7e9f378","tid":2014212,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T03:06:50.000Z","msg":"混血"},{"pid":"cf7656d0afec3d133248e09c9da254f0cbb04b6b","tid":2014212,"uid":119596,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T03:10:00.000Z","msg":"好靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90874a25523e2b6b33eaff0815f58db375e0823f","tid":2014212,"uid":43373,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T03:17:47.000Z","msg":"火加加"}]}